  "body": "### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nUsually we kick the user out to wallet selection on network change because it'll change where we broadcast the transaction, and what chainId to use (among various other things). But in the usecase of signing a message, changing networks does not change how the message will be signed (bad UX?)\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Go to `Sign And Verify Message` tab\r\n2. Sign in with wallet\r\n3. Change networks\r\n4. You will get kicked out to wallet selection\r\n",
